<%- include('../partials/header', { title: 'About Us' }) %>
<div class="content-card">
<div class="wrapper">
  <main class="container">
  <h1>About Our Community Portal</h1>
  <p>
    Welcome to the Community Portal – a digital space where neighbors connect, collaborate, and celebrate local life.
    Whether you're looking for upcoming events, local news, or ways to get involved, this is your go-to hub for all things community.
  </p>

  <p>
    Our mission is to bring people together through shared interests, helpful resources, and meaningful events.
    We believe in fostering connection, supporting each other, and creating a vibrant, inclusive neighborhood where everyone feels at home.
  </p>

  <h2>Meet the Team</h2>
  <p>We're a passionate group of individuals working behind the scenes to keep this portal alive and thriving:</p>

  <ul class="team-list">
    <% team.forEach(member => { %>
      <li><strong><%= member.name %></strong> – <%= member.role %></li>
    <% }) %>
  </ul>
</div>
</main>
</div>
